org.polarsys.chess.patterns.profile.PatternsProfile

Interface PatternsProfilePackage.Literals

  • Enclosing interface:
    PatternsProfilePackage

    public static interface PatternsProfilePackage.Literals
    Defines literals for the meta objects that represent
    • each class,
    • each feature of each class,
    • each operation of each class,
    • each enum,
    • and each data type
